text: The Other Woman is a 1954 American crime drama movie. It was directed by Hugo Haas (who also stars). Other actors include Cleo Moore, Lance Fuller, John Qualen, and Lucille Barkley. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1954 drama movies Category:1954 crime movies Category:American crime drama movies Category:Movies directed by Hugo Haas
